PKPD_ODE_multi_doses_populationFIM

PFIM 5.0

Date: 2023-02-06

Model equations

Model responses: 

RespPK = C1
RespPD = C2

Model equations (for the first dose): 

Deriv_C1 = (dose_RespPK * ka * exp(-(ka * t)) - Cl * C1)/V 
Deriv_C2 = Rin * (1 - (C1)/(C1 + C50)) - kout * C2

Error model

Responses \(\sigma_{slope}\) \(\sigma_{inter}\)
RespPK 0.07 0.6
RespPD 0 4
